<script>
function readFile(aObj){
	var trObj = jQuery(aObj).parent().parent();
        var canRead = trObj.parent().parent().attr("canRead");
        if(canRead && canRead == "no"){
                return false;
        }
	var fileId;
	var sealedFileId = trObj.find('td[icode="SEALED_FILE_ID"]').text();
	var fileName = "";
	if(sealedFileId.length > 0) {
		fileId = sealedFileId;
		fileName = trObj.find('td[icode="DIS_NAME"]').text() + ".pdf";
	} else {
		fileId = trObj.find('td[icode="YY_FILE_ID"]').text();
		fileName = trObj.find('td[icode="FILE_NAME"]').text();
	}
	
	RHFile.read(fileId, fileName);
}
</script>
